name: ONLY INTERNATIONAL HEAVY ARRIVALS at Vancouver Airport (YVR) [4K]
description:
Vancouver International Airport is the second-busiest airport in Canada, and has plenty of international traffic throughout each day, from both and Europe and Asia.

Here's just a few of their regulars landing on runway 26R on a beautiful sunny day in May 2022!
